node.text:
Video by @aerowanderer Go Follow 🙌🏻 / Air India One @boeing B777-300ER approaching and going around as part of its training exercises in Chennai. The aircraft was registered as K7067 and formerly operated for Air India as VT-ALW. This was arriving from Kolkata. This was taken during passing thunderstorms.
.
.
#aviation #aviationdaily #instagramaviation #instaplane #airplanes #avgeek #aircraft #megaplane #aviationlovers #aviationphotography #pilot #plane #landing  #aviationdaily #aviationphoto #pilot #aviationlove #airport #airplane
